      "writtenOn": "2018-10-09T05:22:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "it is set, but reporting an error from outside of a stage would possibly be ugly:\n\n- we can\u0027t call either panic or s.Fatal, since those would make the main goroutine panic or exit\n- we could call s.Error, but then we\u0027d need to manually close ch before returning\n\nso treating this as a setup error seemed like the cleanest approach to me, but let me know if you disagree.",
