      "writtenOn": "2018-10-09T03:24:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This means: if cfg.SetupFunc succeeded but tst.Pre.Prepare() failed, then CleanupFunc is not called. CleanupFunc is often installed to clean up what SetupFunc has done, so I think we want to run CleanupFunc in this case. WDYT?",
