      "writtenOn": "2018-10-09T05:22:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "actually, the only use of CleanupFunc so far isn\u0027t really cleanup -- it\u0027s to call faillog.SaveIfError in tast/bundle/local.go. maybe we should rename this to PostRunFunc? i don\u0027t have strong feelings about whether it should run before or after the precondition\u0027s Close method in that case.",
      "parentUuid": "72f82cfb_5fd0f83a",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 194,
