      "message": "Can\u0027t we do this more simply by pair comparison?\n\n sort.Slice(tests, func(i, j int) bool {\n   ti :\u003d tests[i]\n   tj :\u003d tests[j]\n   var pi, pj string\n   if ti.Pre !\u003d nil {\n     pi \u003d ti.Pre.String()\n   }\n   if tj.Pre !\u003d nil {\n     pj \u003d tj.Pre.String()\n   }\n   if pi !\u003d pj {\n     return pi \u003c pj\n   }\n   return ti.Name \u003c tj.Name\n })",
